---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Experiencias | Luxury Moments">
  <main class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center px-6 overflow-hidden" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1a1111 0%, #050505 100%);">
    
    <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-[#C5A059] opacity-[0.05] blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>

    <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-5xl py-20 flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="backdrop-blur-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/[0.05] p-8 md:p-16 rounded-[40px] shadow-2xl text-center">
        
        <p class="font-sans text-[#C5A059] tracking-[0.6em] text-[10px] md:text-[12px] uppercase mb-8 opacity-80">
          Curaduría de Momentos
        </p>
        
        <h1 class="font-premium text-5xl md:text-8xl text-white mb-10 tracking-tight leading-none">
          EXPERIENCIAS <br/>
          <span class="italic text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-[#F2D184] via-[#C5A059] to-[#8C6D2E]">
            Sin Límites
          </span>
        </h1>

        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mb-10">
            <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#C5A059]/30 self-center"></div>
            <span class="font-sans text-[10px] text-[#C5A059] uppercase tracking-widest">Sensorial · Privado · Único</span>
            <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#C5A059]/30 self-center"></div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-white/60 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14 font-light">
          Desde catas privadas de destilados de colección hasta talleres de maridaje artesanal. Creamos atmósferas donde el tiempo se detiene y el detalle es el protagonista absoluto.
        </p>

        <a href="https://wa.me/51953435738" target="_blank" class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-14 py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#C5A059] to-[#8C6D2E] rounded-full transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(197,160,89,0.3)]">
          <span class="font-sans text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] text-black font-bold uppercase">Agendar Experiencia VIP</span>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-black transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>